Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Tougher smoking warnings
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xd4j
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 27 May 1984
Cigarette packaging to carry tougher health warnings as more research is publicised into the effects of passive smoking. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less